These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, corn
1. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating corn##1
2. the person eating corn is not to the right of the person eating corn##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Food   | corn | zucchini |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, blend
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the left of the blend-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Cigar   | blend | tiparillo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, paramedic
1. the architect is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5
2. the paramedic is on the left or right of the architect##3
3. the architect is not to the right of the architect##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Job   | architect | paramedic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
