1. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##8
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Sport   | swimming | skateboarding |

